The '''Marine Strategy Framework Directive''' (MSFD; full title: ''Directive 2008/56/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 17 June 2008 establishing a framework for community action in the field of marine environmental policy'') is a [[Directive (European Union)|European Directive]] aimed at achieving or maintaining [[Good Environmental Status]] in European seas.<ref>[http://ec.europa.eu/environment/marine/eu-coast-and-marine-policy/marine-strategy-framework-directive/index_en.htm European Commission - Legislation: The Marine Directive]</ref>

